Hi <%= @assignee.name %>,

You have been assigned a new task:

<%= @task.title %>
<% if @task.description.present? %>
Description: <%= @task.description %>
<% end %>

Task Type: <%= @task.task_type.titleize %>
Priority: <%= @task.priority.titleize %>
<% if @task.due_date.present? %>
Due Date: <%= @task.due_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %>
<% end %>

<% if @conversation.present? %>
Related to conversation: <%= @conversation.display_id %>
<% elsif @contact.present? %>
Related to contact: <%= @contact.name %>
<% end %>

Please complete this task at your earliest convenience.

Best regards,
<%= @account_name %> Team
